Package com.soen6441.risk_game_u14.state

Class Startup

java.lang.Object
com.soen6441.risk_game_u14.state.Phase
com.soen6441.risk_game_u14.state.Startup
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Startup extends Phase implements Serializable
The Startup Phase extends the phase class and implements all the methods suitable for that particular phase. It returns invalid command for others which are not compatible with this phase
